{"tid":934290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【灣區風情】孟晚舟其實贏了！﹙程凱﹚","createTime":"2018-12-09T07:12:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-09T14:35:20.000Z","uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d54ae6a0ce054c0494380ba578108d7aeb102af0","tid":934290,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T07:12:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【灣區風情】孟晚舟其實贏了！﹙程凱﹚</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181209/59009961\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181209%2F59009961&d=PSRvB71USbKvCiCuTlXTSS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=815b8d62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181209%2F59009961&h=f36a7780\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181209/59009961</a><br />\n<br />\n「孟晚舟其實贏了！」這是一篇內地支持華為太子女的文章標題，內文形容孟晚舟在溫哥華法庭上「不懼、不畏、不怒」「從容自若、淡定自如」，要知道中國人面對委屈，拍檯大吵大鬧唱國歌已是指定動作，可是孟晚舟沒有喊打喊殺，法庭上「挺直腰板」、「不時露出笑容」，更有「泰山崩於前而眼不瞬」的沉著，雖還未勝訴，但表現已戰勝了自己，沒有辜負「華為最厲害女人」的稱號，因此孟晚舟其實贏了！<br />\n<br />\n中國的精神勝利法不用多介紹，自孟晚舟在加拿大被捕，內地由外交部以至媒體、網民全都槍口一致對外，更未審早認定孟晚舟是無辜的。有官方撐腰，愛國憤青便無懼炒車盲撐，就算孟晚舟擁有加拿大籍及香港身份證，根本不可能擁有中國護照，但外交部話孟晚舟是中國籍就是中國籍，立即速遞一本中國護照給她都無問題，總之孟晚舟是中國人，她無罪。<br />\n<br />\n可是，加拿大掌握證據敢於告上法庭，至今不肯放人，中國能做的就只有鼓動國內民族情緒，聲稱被捕是外國勢力亡我之心不死，中國人被種族歧視，西方國怕強國掘起而插贓嫁禍的卑劣流氓手段。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">孟晚舟現在已是國家對抗外敵的巾幗英雄，由於戰狼吳京傳逃稅被罵假愛國，孟晚舟正好取而代之團結國家，而華為更是代表中國科技站起來對抗美國的民族企業。有指習近平在G20上早知孟晚舟會被捕，他沒有阻止或者就是將計就計，在中美貿易戰節節敗退下，靠孟晚舟挽回一下聲望。</span><br />\n<br />\n程凱"},{"pid":"c770f95ca4c059df22d4047f039a0a068de9a1c7","tid":934290,"uid":93986,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T07:17:02.000Z","msg":"阿Q精神"},{"pid":"a4d0d0bcf8948789f5b66e6b55a95d5b219dcf40","tid":934290,"uid":50457,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T07:19:49.000Z","msg":"慢慢周站在犯人欄不發一言<br />\n<br />\n竟然咁都可以吹到幾百字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n孔子再世都唔夠你玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd1e18365534772a4457f061f6f7e95a595f4eef","tid":934290,"uid":61484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T07:21:03.000Z","msg":"為左講個贏字可以去到幾盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b15fab18c729e006baac3f634ee4c2177081fbde","tid":934290,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T07:25:59.000Z","msg":"程凱有guts<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85843ddd4973e27dab1f08c718a7bdca2e3d5d14","tid":934290,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T07:28:21.000Z","msg":"贏了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f78fe284d998a3a5000a67482f3fe04874ce82bd","tid":934290,"uid":89909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T07:32:03.000Z","msg":"贏國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6270b94458cba9486ac7aea0a24c2d569e6d11b0","tid":934290,"uid":45518,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T07:32:11.000Z","msg":"愛國愛到咁多加拿大物業<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d08123b98d3ead18475b5ba2e9089267d8cbbeeb","tid":934290,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T07:35:49.000Z","msg":"同日本皇軍打到1945年都仲覺得本土決戰係有機會贏美軍一樣戇鳩"},{"pid":"39c6178798614fe3d8eeff4935c37973287b10ee","tid":934290,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r